range(50): data.append(int(sh.recvline()[:-1])) #print(data) data.reverse() sh.recvuntil("[+]c = ") c = int(sh.recvuntil("n")[:-1]) m="" for i in data: if c>=i: m+='1' c-=i else: m+='0' print c if enc(data,int(m,2)) : m = m[::-1] m = int(m,2) sh.sendline(hex(m)[2:]) sh.recvuntil("knapsack.n") data=[] for _ in range(100): data.append(int(sh.recvline()[:-1])) print("a = "+str(data).replace("L","")) sh.recvuntil("[+]c = ") c = int(sh.recvuntil("n")[:-1]) print("s = "+str(c)) sh.interactive() æ‹¿åˆ°æ•°æ®äº†å»ç”¨sageè§£å¯† a = #å¡«å…¥åºåˆ—a s = #å¡«å…¥å¯†æ–‡å€¼ m=[] for
